Actions for Wolves (diga) on the Bathurst and Bluenose-East Barren-ground", "Caribou Herd Winter Ranges: 2021 2024.\" - (nkwr;,)", "For many years now, Dehq~ and other Sahtu communities have been expressing their concerns regarding", "diga (wolf) culls to ENR and co-management bodies including the Sahtu Renwable Resources Board", "(SRRB) and the Wek'eezhii Renewable Resources Board (WRRB). At the 2016 SRRB hearing on", "Bluenose East, Elders from all Sahtu communities described the important relationship between diga 5", "and 1ekw~ (caribou). The Elders explained that the diga keep the 1ekwlr populations healthy, that killing", "all the diga might actually wipe out the 1ekw~. and that the diga must be respected. This relationship is", "also described in Dehqfs Belarew1ie Gots'~ 7ekw~, or caribou conservation plan, which was formally", "approved as a community conservation plan by the SRRB and was accepted and endorsed by the Minister", "of the Environment and Natural Resources in 2016."], "bbox": [[0.347075, 0.154379, 0.43521299999999996, 0.028861], [0.453186, 0.182323, 0.087723, 0.017348], [0.427859, 0.199141, 0.13634199999999996, 0.017348], [0.352582, 0.216414, 0.28762800000000005, 0.017348], [0.388072, 0.233687, 0.215229, 0.017348], [0.113366, 0.266748, 0.12509, 0.017349], [0.113431, 0.321306, 0.248008, 0.017349], [0.113464, 0.348566, 0.29096900000000003, 0.017349], [0.114118, 0.376293, 0.18186000000000002, 0.017349], [0.113497, 0.393111, 0.19650299999999998, 0.017349], [0.113431, 0.420839, 0.19666500000000003, 0.017349], [0.11232, 0.47551, 0.10899400000000001, 0.017421], [0.112271, 0.530106, 0.43616900000000003, 0.018537], [0.112271, 0.584929, 0.146229, 0.017349], [0.112206, 0.639929, 0.692685, 0.017349], [0.112255, 0.657657, 0.709031, 0.017421], [0.1125, 0.675055, 0.744116, 0.017421], [0.11317, 0.690192, 0.12329999999999998, 0.019579], [0.112271, 0.746748, 0.756001, 0.017349], [0.11219, 0.76402, 0.726367, 0.017349], [0.112157, 0.781293, 0.704512, 0.017349], [0.